{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"52b2b7d8dd","title":"对陈叔通来信的复信和批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9f99bc2da5","index":1,"year":1953,"month":5,"day":19,"articleId":"52b2b7d8dd"},{"id":"fd32b4b46e","index":0,"year":1953,"month":5,"day":18,"articleId":"52b2b7d8dd"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji33","name":"毛泽东全集第33卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/33-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji33":{"comments":[{"id":"611f9419f6","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"52b2b7d8dd","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陈叔通，当时任中华全国工商业联合会筹备委员会主任委员、政协全国委员会副主席。"},{"id":"9466f42c9d","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"52b2b7d8dd","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指陈叔通1953年5月9日给毛泽东的信。信中说：“送呈上月召集六省工商联秘书长汇报资料一份，文参考资料第干期至第十二期共三份，请备查阅。现在是到了要求得解决的阶段。税收方面，政府已作很大的努力。劳资关系，经过这次总工会第七次大会，必有很大的改善。同时，资方应该改造思想，求其在己。至于资金问题，只要公私、劳资关系搞好，可能有办法，即游资、睡资亦可能投入。打通销路，积压亦得到解决。依赖贷款不是办法。总的说来，国营要加强领导，私营要先了解政策。"},{"id":"394f40d32c","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"52b2b7d8dd","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"小平，即邓小平，当时任政务院副总理。"},{"id":"3482152c38","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"52b2b7d8dd","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李维汉，当时任中共中央统战部部长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"a482c498cf","type":"title","text":"对陈叔通\"来信的复信和批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"52b2b7d8dd"},{"id":"611f9419f6","type":"paragraph","text":"叔通先生","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"52b2b7d8dd"},{"id":"9466f42c9d","type":"paragraph","text":"五月九日惠书以及附件数份，均已收到，甚为感谢。承示各点，我以为是正确的。此复。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"52b2b7d8dd"},{"id":"394f40d32c","type":"paragraph","text":"顺致敬意","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"52b2b7d8dd"},{"id":"3482152c38","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"52b2b7d8dd"},{"id":"64b3ba463f","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五三年五月十八日周总理、小平叫同志阅，交李维汉同志：","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"52b2b7d8dd"},{"id":"f0235533ce","type":"paragraph","text":"此数件阅后，请维汉登入《零讯》。原件用后还我。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"52b2b7d8dd"},{"id":"24ecd4d6d3","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"52b2b7d8dd"},{"id":"9d66af2d15","type":"paragraph","text":"五月十九日","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"52b2b7d8dd"}],"page":{"id":"8385463371","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"52b2b7d8dd","start":173,"end":175}}}},"__N_SSG":true}